{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b78de9264c","title":"关于暂停炮击和发表《告台湾同胞书》给彭德怀、黄克诚的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c4861ba49","index":1,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":6,"articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"68b435a843","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":5,"articleId":"b78de9264c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"37babb8a53","name":"叶飞","type":"人物"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"fc720a2067","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。黄克诚，当时任中共中央军委秘书长、国防部副部长。"},{"id":"c0c4b0c83e","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"叶飞，当时任中国人民解放军福州军区政治委员。韩先楚，当时任中国人民解放军福州军区司令员。"},{"id":"a71356aa59","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指毛泽东起草的、准备以国防部部长彭德怀名义发表的《告台湾同胞书》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"dbac380260","type":"title","text":"关于暂停炮击和发表《告台湾同胞书给彭德怀、黄克诚“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"fc720a2067","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀、克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"c0c4b0c83e","type":"paragraph","text":"不管有无美机美舰护航，十月六、七两日，我军一炮不发；故方向我炮击，我也一炮不还。假旗息鼓，观察两天，再作道理。空军必须防卫，但不出海。还有一事：两天中，不要发表公开声明，因为情况如何，尚待看清。以上请即令行。或者即以此信转发叶飞、韩先楚”","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"a71356aa59","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"62cc3f132d","type":"paragraph","text":"十月五日上午八时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"5489163ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"此件处理后，送总理一阅彭、黄，请发韩、叶”：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"b04ebe2570","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我说不发声明，看两天再说。随后想了一下，还是先作声明为好，所以有告台湾同胞书。此件即将发出，请福建前线广播电台多播几次，为盼！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"d25c58b49a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"ea7ad37b60","type":"paragraph","text":"十月六日上午二时","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"a35fefd285","type":"paragraph","text":"即送克诚办。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"},{"id":"85083961bb","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]彭，指彭德怀。黄，指黄克诚。韩，指韩先楚。叶，指叶飞。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c"}],"page":{"id":"24eec28521","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"b78de9264c","start":294,"end":295}}}},"__N_SSG":true}